values.title: Adding a new version for the transport tutorial for gazebo v2.2+

summary.html:
The current tutorial was using the old calls:

gazebo::load(_argc, _argv);
gazebo::run();
...
gazebo::transport::fini();

and they have to be replaced by:

gazebo::setupClient(_argc, _argv);
...
gazebo::shutdown();
